@Node "Overview" "UMSMailStat.guide/Overview"
@Toc "Main"

What is UMSMailStat?
********************

   UMSMailStat is a tool for creating hitlists about authors and
subjects of a newsgroup found in an UMS-messagebase. UMSMailStat has
its roots in 'TopTen' by Kai Bolay and Jan Geissler, expanding
functionality in many points.

   UMSMailStat is/has been written in Modula-2 (M2Amiga v4.3).


@EndNode

